294
00:12:39,620 --> 00:12:41,080
It looks delicious.

295
00:12:41,980 --> 00:12:44,390
Whoa. You’re eating crispy pork first.

296
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:45,100
Hey.

297
00:12:47,490 --> 00:12:48,620
It’s delicious.

298
00:12:50,190 --> 00:12:51,530
