299
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:56,190
Wow. It’s delicious.

300
00:12:56,230 --> 00:12:57,220
What do you think?

301
00:12:57,700 --> 00:12:58,890
How could I do this?

302
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:02,080
Oh, it’s delicious for real.

303
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,340
See? I told you.

304
00:13:03,370 --> 00:13:04,760
I’ve realized I can cook, too.

305
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:05,930
Pun.

306
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:08,180
